  "prompt": "What is months at level in Accenture?",
  "response": "\"Months at level\" in Accenture refers to the duration that an employee has spent in their current job level or position. Accenture generally has multiple career levels, and tracking the months at level helps in understanding tenure, assessing readiness for promotion, and planning career development paths. Each level has its own responsibilities, expectations, and qualifications, and time spent at a level can be an important factor in performance reviews and progression within the company.",
